# Vercel Web Analytics Configuration - Already Implemented

## Summary
The Vercel Web Analytics has already been fully configured in this Next.js App Router project. No code changes were necessary.

## Current Implementation Status

### ✅ Package Installation
- **Package**: `@vercel/analytics@1.6.1`
- **Status**: Already installed in package.json
- **Location**: `web/package.json` (dependencies section)

### ✅ App Router Configuration
- **File**: `src/app/layout.tsx`
- **Import**: `import { Analytics } from "@vercel/analytics/next"`
- **Implementation**: `<Analytics />` component is placed inside the `<body>` tag, after the `{children}` element

### Implementation Details
The Analytics component is correctly positioned in the root layout file:
```tsx
<body className={...}>
  {children}
  <Analytics />
</body>
```

This follows the official Vercel documentation for Next.js App Router projects.

